1954;;The Golden Idol;;American;;Ford Beebe;;Johnny Sheffield, Anne Kimbell;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Golden_Idol;;Prince Ali wants the Golden Idol of Watusi and hires a ruthless hunter to get it for him. Bomba has the idol and, with the help of Commissioner Barnes, Eli, and a beautiful archeologist, he foils Ali's plans. [Anne Kimbell] Ali and the hunter are noticeably more cold-blooded than most of Bomba's adversaries.